	   <tr><td colspan=2>True, a druid isn't a melee class, but every class should carry a weapon, even if just in their pack. I have my testament (cleric), but when I run OOM during a fight, the melees are sure happy to see me jump in and take a couple hundred pts off the MOB (especially if the mob is getting low on hp, but so are the melees). I even saved a rogue one time by getting the mob to target me, and then she killed it with 1 backstab (and she had less than 1 bubble of life left). There's more than one way to save the melees life, and killing the mob when oom is one of them.<br>Don't underestimate the value of Wisdom casters' melee skills. They may just save you some day.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
